</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns ist fürbraht <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie daz
                        der <expan>S<ex>eicz</ex></expan> Graf, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><gap reason="damaged"/>,</note>
</app>in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz geleyte
                            <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fr<ex>ankfurt</ex></expan> und Meincz
                            <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> und hinweg gefürt sey
                                <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir <app>
<note><gap reason="damaged"/></note>
</app>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> biten und v<app>
<note><gap reason="damaged"/></note>
</app>
<pb facs="#facs_6" id="1v"/>ewr günst und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen
                        seinen gnaden beweisen wöllet, ob der <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, ledig werden möht, als etc.
                        Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab></div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Dem edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                        Pickenbach und <expan>burgrafe<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>Miltenb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>,<lb/><expan>Hanneman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Eͣchter<ex>n</ex></expan>, vicztume czu Asschaffemburg,
                                <expan>ecia<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
